title: Abundantly Free
itunes:title: Abundantly Free
description:
Would you describe yourself as partially free or abundantly free? In this message, be encouraged to stand firm in the freedom that Jesus died for you to have. Hold onto that promise by faith, begin to get in agreement with God. You do not have to settle for partial freedom--abundant freedom is yours in Jesus.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
